<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Nihin Jesuh a tho cang, Hal-le-lu-jah! Minung le vancungmi hna,
 Hal-le-lu-jah! Teinak hla fakpi'n sa u, Hal-le-lu-jah! Van le vawlei mi
 sa u, Hal-le-lu-jah!

[V2]
 Khamhnak rian kha a lim cang, Hal-le-lu-jah! Thihnak ral kha a tei
 cang, Hal-le-lu-jah! Thihnak nih a tlai kho lo, Hal-le-lu-jah! Pa-ra-dais
 kha a hun cang, Hal-le-lu-jah!

[V3]
 Kan Siangpahrang a nung than, Hal-le-lu-jah! Maw thihnak na sivai tah?
 Hal-le-lu-jah! Thihnak in a kan khamh cang, Hal-le-lu-jah! Maw, thlan na
 mi teinak tah? Hal-le-lu-jah!

[V4]
 Khrih kan hruaitu kan zulh lai, Hallelujah! Thangthatmi kan Bawipa cu,
 Hal-le-lu-jah! Amah bang kan tho than lai, Hal-le-lu-jah! Teinak in
 teinak chin ah, Hal-le-lu-jah!</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
<title>NIHIN KHRIH A THO THAN CH144</title>
<hymn_number>144</hymn_number>
</song>